## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] CLI args have highest priority
- [ ] Environment variables checked second
- [ ] Project config (.beads/config.yaml) checked third
- [ ] User config (~/.config/br/config.yaml) checked fourth
- [ ] SQLite config table checked fifth (for eligible keys)
- [ ] Hard-coded defaults used last
- [ ] YAML-only keys never read from SQLite
- [ ] ConfigSource tracks where value came from
- [ ] Environment variable expansion in YAML (${VAR:-default})
- [ ] Type coercion (string to bool, string to int)

